{"tid":1432433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點算 我真係好撚憎啲廢老","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:20:15.000Z","uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f26b5acf429f1fbc20c9e0373b71da5eb1f128","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"頭先喺葵廣買嘢<br />\n身後有幾個死八婆廢老<br />\n又喺度鬧啲後生仔<br />\n「都唔知讀乜撚嘢書嘅讀到咁」<br />\n「呢班仆街，八婆」<br />\n啲説話真係好撚難聽<br />\n好撚不值班細路咁樣俾佢地話<br />\n忍唔撚住擰轉面睥咗班廢老一眼<br />\n哈佢哋又即刻靜咗一下望住我喎<br />\n然後又繼續講但擺明係講俾我聽<br />\n「唔好理佢啫 繼續講」<br />\n<br />\n屌你三條死八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚後悔當時唔撚夠膽屌鳩返佢哋<br />\n唯有上黎圍吓爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底遇到呢啲廢柴廢老<br />\n應唔應該屌鳩返佢哋<br />\n成日喺街聽到真係谷撚到就黎爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴絲們教吓路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709460e55356428e9cf3d99e02e2728e8394968b","tid":1432433,"uid":182827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"嘩係啦<br />\n鬼叫你地啲老母唔撚識教生啲廢青出黎<br />\n如果第時香港有再教育營<br />\n第一個拉你班老母入去鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a8165c4bd4994bdac341d9d7f9aaafcce3e07d","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"709460e55356428e9cf3d99e02e2728e8394968b","tid":1432433,"uid":182827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"嘩係啦<br />\n鬼叫你地啲老母唔撚識教生啲廢青出黎<br />\n如果第時香港有再教育營<br />\n第一個拉你班老母入去鞭屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:52:58.000Z","msg":"呢個唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有巴打話要藍過佢哋<br />\n但我真係唔係好知啲廢老個豬腦諗啲咩<br />\n驚轉唔切佢哋個弱智mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c54c40005c18ece6523ca71ed8a603b5776c2a7","tid":1432433,"uid":92332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"葵廣特別多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24d84c655fc0594220936bd9998f32f0670a773","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c54c40005c18ece6523ca71ed8a603b5776c2a7","tid":1432433,"uid":92332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"葵廣特別多廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:59:58.000Z","msg":"係呀我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚想屌鳩柒佢哋<br />\n成班個腦都唔撚用嘅<br />\n唔撚關心個社會發生咩事<br />\n淨係識用自己自撚私嘅心態去以己度人<br />\n梗係成世都唔會明啦<br />\n畜生點會有人類嘅思想<br />\n<br />\n唉屌宜家就講到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好炆自己真係唔識同人嗌交"},{"pid":"a24331ff7e878ce73595f748fb9031b434544af8","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fb76c5b7d743326b533e1eb3d861846dae8b4d0","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d55349de1ea9272d413623e15df985e52e300b9b","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:03:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b8b21c01885903dd6200fdef6e7130badfd07aca","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c241b6195330c0b340384d0208fe2e87b6c00194","tid":1432433,"uid":164382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T09:20:15.000Z","msg":"真係好炆自己做乜咁撚淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}